bb-assist (0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * One less druidpage to USB with IP static
  * ifup interface in USB
  * changes in dependencies
  * added gnome help (only in Spanish)
  * added better clean of old configurations in /etc/network/interfaces
  * check if correct USB vendor/product is connected
  * More examples and devel doc

